            <h3 class="ec-howwork__title">No Tools</h3>
            <p class="ec-howwork__body">Most growing brands run ops on spreadsheets, Shopify exports, and memory. We centralize everything into a single source of truth, build the workflows around it, and take over the daily, weekly, and monthly cadences.</p>
